history.content:
Gradescope has a built in small grace period. It's not publicized, for obvious reasons.

Gradescope is a company. You can contact the company. They may or may not respond.

Has anyone ever been able to submit an assignment on Gradescope slightly after the deadline (a grace period)? I remember being able to do this for one of my classes, but apparently I shouldn't be able to?

How can I contact Gradescope to request internal information from Gradescope? Is anyone at Cal directly in charge of it?
history.subject: Gradescope Grace Period
